  <source>National Taiwan University Hospital</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the PK/PD parameters, safety and efficacy of
      extended infusion of beta-lactams in intensive care patients who are infected with
      Gram-negative bacteremia or pneumonia at National Taiwan University Hospital (NTUH).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
